<!DOCTYPE html>
	<head>
		<title>Experimental</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/custom.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/normalize.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/skeleton.css">
	</head>
	<header class="header-1">
    <nav>
      <div class="container">
          <ul class="main-nav js--main-nav">
              <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="#programs" class="js--scroll-to-contact">About</a></li>
              <li><a href="#nutrition" class="js--scroll-to-main-nav">Articles</a></li>
              <li><a href="#coaches" class="js--scroll-to-fan-pics">Videos</a></li>
              <li><a href="#contact" class="js--scroll-to-book">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
          <a class="mobile-nav-icon js--nav-icon"><i class="ion-navicon"></i></a>
      </div>
    </nav>
	<body>
		<div class="section_1">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="eight columns">
					<% @articles.each_with_index do |article, index| %>
					<h3 class="article-title"><%=link_to article.title, article_path(article) %></h3>
					<i class="date-copy"><%= time_ago_in_words(article.created_at) %> ago, by Mark Hustad</i>
					<% if article.image.present? %>
					<%= image_tag article.image.url(:large), :class => "u-max-full-width article-image-index" %>
					<% end %>
						<p class="article-paragraph"><%= simple_format(index.zero? ?  article.body : truncate(article.body, length: 300)) %></p>
						<p class="read-more"><%= link_to 'read more', article_path(article) unless index.zero? %></p>
						<% end %>
						<%= will_paginate @articles %>
						
					</div>
					<div class="four columns">
					<h3 class="article-title">New Promotion</h3>
						<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vestibulum imperdiet nisl id venenatis aliquam. Phasellus ullamcorper eget enim vel aliquam. Integer vel tincidunt risus, sed ultrices tellus. Proin sit amet aliquet orci, in scelerisque risus.</p>
						<ul class="sidebar_links">
							<li><a href="#">Recent News</a></li>
							<li><a href="#">Popular Articles</a></li>
							<li><a href="#">Reviews</a></li>
							<li><a href="#">Games</a></li>
							<li><a href="#">Streaming</a></li>
						</ul>
						<% if logged_in? %>
							<p>Current User: <%= (current_user.name) %><br>
           		<%=link_to 'create new article', new_article_path %><br>
           		<%=link_to 'Logout', logout_path, method: "delete" %><br>
           		<% else %>
           		<%=link_to 'Login', login_path %></p>
           		<% end %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.2/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/custom.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>